a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"https://mila.quebec/yoshua-bengio/\">Yoshua Bengio</a>, at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cs.mcgill.ca/\">School of Computer Science</a>&nbsp;of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/\">McGill University</a>. In 2020, I graduated as a MSc., advised by <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~chang/\">Xiao-Wen Chang</a>, with CGPA 4.0/4.0.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":358,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/homepage/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2/haiper/\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":15,\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"full\",\"imageFill\":false} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:15% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/haiperai/\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Haiper.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-358 size-full\"/></a></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">I am a research scientist (part-time) at <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/haiperai/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/haiperai/\">Haiper</a>, working with <a href=\"https://ziyuw.github.io/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://ziyuw.github.io/\">Ziyu Wang</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/yishumiao\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://sites.google.com/view/yishumiao\">Yishu Miao</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":359,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/homepage/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2/ms/\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"