ness.png\" alt=\"\"> I am currently working on conscious planning with Prof.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mila.quebec/yoshua-bengio/\">Yoshua Bengio</a>&nbsp;and Prof.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\"><img class=\"wp-image-74\" style=\"width: 25px;\" src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/DLUT_logo.png\" alt=\"\"> I studied as an undergrad at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.dlut.edu.cn/\">Dalian University of Technology</a>, with major in Computer Science and Technology, and minor in Creative Practices (humanoid robotics), 2014 to 2018. I received the award of Distinguished Student Researcher (the only one for class 2018) and graduated with 90+ percentage (CGPA 4.0/4.0).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"33.33%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\"><!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CN6Jb6clODX/\",\"type\":\"rich\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"instagram\",\"responsive\":true} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-instagram wp-block-embed-instagram\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CN6Jb6clODX/\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Bonjour! Hello! 你好!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-04-21 18:00:58', '2021-04-21 22:00:58', '', 36, 'http://localhost/homepage/?p=179', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(181, 1, '2021-04-21 18:11:21', '2021-04-21 22:11:21', '<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":6,\"textColor\":\"accent\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-align-center has-accent-color has-text-color\">DISCOVERING INTELLIGENCE VIA COMPUTATION</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":71,\"width\":100} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/logo_MILA-180x180-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-71\" width=\"100\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am a researcher at <a href=\"https://mila.quebec/en/\">Mila</a> (Quebec AI Institute) interested in the learning aspects of AI, especially reinforcement learning and conscious processing.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":72,\"width\":100} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/McGill-Bird.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-72\" width=\"100\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am a Ph.D. student of Prof. <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a> and Prof. <a href=\"https://mila.quebec/yoshua-bengio/\">Yoshua Bengio</a>, at <a href=\"http://cs.mcgill.ca/\">School of Computer Science</a> of <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/\">McGill University</a>. In summer 2020, I graduated as a MSc., under Prof. <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a> and Prof. <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~chang/\">Xiao-Wen Chang</a>, with CGPA 4.0/4.0.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":73,\"width\":100} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Consciousness.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-73\" width=\"100\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -